snippet.title: Garden Witch Life | Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Restore the magic of a vacant witch house, cultivate a garden where adorable creatures roam freely, and create delectable recipes to share with the community. Experience all of this and more when #GardenWitchLife launches on PC, PS5, and Xbox Series X|S later this year. #cozygame #indiegame

About SOEDESCO:
SOEDESCO is an independent video game developer, publisher, and distributor founded in 2002 by Soedesh Chauthi with its headquarters in Rotterdam, the Netherlands, and offices in Madrid, Spain & Pilsen, Czech Republic. We deliver creative content across multiple genres and platforms for a worldwide audience in physical and digital formats.
